snippet.title: PSP - Jak and Daxter: The Lost Frontier - LongPlay [4K]🔴
snippet.description:
PSP - Jak and Daxter: The Lost Frontier - LongPlay [4K]🔴

Well this is a very nice game just like other Jak and Daxter games, it has very nice graphics, music and game verity.
However it has know problems that is terrible camera and not the best controls. The game is scripted heavily even the jumps are scripted so it is hard to get used to.
Overall a nice game that i recommend.

"Despite the disappointing Dark Daxter levels and the sometimes-troublesome camera, The Lost Frontier lives up to the Jak and Daxter name with some solid and varied gameplay, challenging platforming, and a great mix of ground and aerial combat. These combined elements help to breathe new life into the series while not straying too far from the familiar wacky adventures of this butt-kicking duo. " - GameSpot

Metacritic - 71%
